<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٥ -<span class="c5"> بَاب:</span> مَنْ نَامَ أَوَّلَ اللَّيْلِ وَأَحْيَا آخِرَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ سَلْمَانُ لِأَبِي الدَّرْدَاءِ <span class="special">﵄</span>:</span> نَمْ، فَلَمَّا كَانَ مِنْ آخِرِ اللَّيْلِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قُمْ.<span class="c5"> قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>:</span> <span class="c2">(صَدَقَ سَلْمَانُ)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
